Redis operations Operations


set <key> <value> - Set the key with the value

get <key> - get the value  for the key

del <key> - deletes the key and the value

mset <key> <value> <key> <value> - Multiple set operations

gset <key> <key> <key> - Multiple get operations

exist <key> - check if the key exist in Map.

expire <key> <duration in sec> - make the key expire within a specific time.

persist <key> - removes the expiry

set <key> <value> [ex|px] duration - set the key and value along with the expiry time line or duration. ex - seconds px -milli seconds
